        <h1>Revision History</h1>

        <h2>Version numbering</h2>
        <p>The Client Container uses the following version numbering scheme:
            <br/>
            <strong>MAJOR.MINOR.PATCH (RELEASE_DATE)</strong>
        </p>
        <p>
            <strong>MAJOR</strong>
            version numbers are reserved for significant functional upgrades with breaking API changes.
            <br/>
            <strong>MINOR</strong>
            version numbers are incremented for functional upgrades with backwards compatibility.
            <br/>
            <strong>PATCH</strong>
            version numbers are incremented for bug fixes and improvements.
        </p>
        <p>
            <strong>NB</strong>: Not all versions of the Client Container are tagged for release as supported versions.
            Releases are selected and labelled builds.
        </p>

